Nollywood actress, Uche Jombo has reacted to the rumours about the health status of her fellow colleague in the industry, Genevieve Nnaji. An Instagram user, @adie_godwin20 tagged Jombo to a comment saying, “Please check on her and know if she is okay. I know she is ur best friend.” Jombo replied by saying “How about you don’t believe everything you see on social media?” -Advertisement- Recall that Nnaji deleted her pictures and video on her official Instagram page with 8.5m followers after she shared some cryptic messages which led to rumours of the actress battling mental illness. However, the actress debunked the rumours by sharing a video of herself painting a picture to show that she is alright.